name: telll
body:
### Welcome to telll.
Telll, inline multi media links.

Telll implements a non intrusive ads system. The actual version is Nyquist 0.17.

Terms of Service:
https://github.com/Telll/telll.github.io/wiki/Telll-Terms-of-Service

See docs:
http://telll.github.io/SDK

See the code and download:
https://github.com/Telll/SDK

Open webapp:
http://webapp.telll.me/

(user: mock_01 and pass: blablabla)

### Authors and Contributors
- 2015, Feb - Monsenhor <filipo@kobkob.org> begins telll development.
- 2015, Jun - Monsenhor <filipo@kobkob.org> published first demo (Shanon 0.14)
- 2015, Ago - FCO <fernandocorrea@gmail.com> begins REST and Websockets in TWS - Mojolicious
- 2015, Nov - Monsenhor <filipo@kobkob.org> first production version (Nyquist 0.16) 

### Support or Contact
Ask Monsenhor:
    Ricardo Filipo (filipo@telll.me || filipo@kobkob.org)

### Participate
Clone here:
https://github.com/Telll/SDK

Ask Monsenhor:
    Ricardo Filipo (filipo@telll.me || filipo@kobkob.org)
